  "notes": [
    "1. This event should be emitted *after* inventory has been decremented (or at least after the deltas are known).",
    "2. Automation may listen to this to trigger preservation suggestions, storehouse replenishment, or to update meal analytics dashboards.",
    "3. If featureFlags.familyFundMode=true, a listener (like src/events/eventMappers.js) can map this to hub:meal.executed and send it to the Hub.",
    "4. Always include `sessionId` so the UI can navigate back to the completed session.",
    "5. Keep JSON-only (no $schema) to avoid VS Code schema fetch errors."
